name: lonely celebration - #HENdonesia
description:
It’s a tradition for Indonesian to celebrate Independence Day by participating in games and competitions. One of the famous games that usually held in the local neighbourhood is the cracker (krupuk) eating competition. This artwork is a representation of what i feel right now, staying still inside and celebrating the festivities alongside my imaginary friend 💀 

Made with procreate + adobe after effects + krupuk
